00074 void SCTPMessage::addChunk(cPacket* msg)
00075 {
00076     char str[256];
00077     take(msg);
00078     if (this->chunkList.size()<9)
00079     {
00080         strcpy(str, this->getName());
00081         snprintf(str, sizeof(str), "%s %s",this->getName(), msg->getName());
00082         this->setName(str);
00083     }
00084     this->setBitLength(this->getBitLength()+ADD_PADDING(msg->getBitLength()/8)*8);
00085     chunkList.push_back(msg);
00086 }
